thread.title: BRIEF-Yapi Kredi FY 2017 Net Profit Up At 3.61 Bln Lira

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Yapi Kredi FY 2017 Net Profit Up At 3.61 Bln Lira
text:
Feb 6 (Reuters) - YAPI KREDI:
* FY 2017 NET INTEREST INCOME OF 9.21 BILLION LIRA VERSUS 7.63 BILLION LIRA YEAR AGO
* FY 2017 UNCONSOLIDATED NET PROFIT OF 3.61 BILLION LIRA VERSUS 2.93 BILLION LIRA YEAR AGO
* FY 2017 NET FEE AND COMMISSION INCOME 3.14 BILLION LIRA VERSUS 2.83 MILLION LIRA YEAR AGO
* NON-PERFORMING LOANS AT END OF 2017 AT 9.02 BILLION LIRA VERSUS 8.71 BILLION LIRA AT END-DEC. 2016 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
